title: Sidsel Owren
text:
Sidsel Owren is a Norwegian <a href="ski-orienteering">ski-orienteering</a> competitor. 
She won a bronze medal in the relay event at the 1982 <a href="World%20Ski%20Orienteering%20Championships">World Ski Orienteering Championships</a> in Austria, together with <a href="Toril%20Hallan">Toril Hallan</a> and <a href="Ranveig%20Narbuvold">Ranveig Narbuvold</a>, and placed eleventh in the individual event.
